# Java Program

```java
public class Main {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        int n = 5;

        System.out.println(n << 1); // 10
        System.out.println(n << 2); // 20

        System.out.println(20 >> 1); // 10
        System.out.println(20 >> 2); // 5
    }
}
```

