# Four Most Important Operations

## Check kth Bit

```java
(n & (1 << k)) != 0
```

Meaning:

```text
Bit is ON ?
```

---

## Set kth Bit

```java
n | (1 << k)
```

Meaning:

```text
Turn bit ON
```

---

## Clear kth Bit

```java
n & ~(1 << k)
```

Meaning:

```text
Turn bit OFF
```

---

## Toggle kth Bit

```java
n ^ (1 << k)
```

Meaning:

```text
0 -> 1
1 -> 0
```

